div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/arif10\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a28856525b7b39a6c244c947eee21868?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a28856525b7b39a6c244c947eee21868?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/arif10\" class=\"reviewer-name\">arif10</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Ive been using this plugin for a long time and it is great. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">simple, facile</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/eoik\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ecf565e23dd792141a185adefa7dc190?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ecf565e23dd792141a185adefa7dc190?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/eoik\" class=\"reviewer-name\">eoik</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 13, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Tout fonctionne trs bien, trs simplement. Merci beaucoup  l\'auteur du plugin. \n\nPrcision, pour rcuprer un message d\'erreur quand on utilise la case  cocher d\'acceptation des conditions, il faut :\n\nAu niveau du formulaire ajouter : \n[acceptance your-consent] En soumettant ce formulaire, jaccepte que mes informations soient utilises exclusivement dans le cadre de ma demande et de la relation commerciale thique et personnalise qui pourrait en dcouler si je le souhaite.  [/acceptance]\n\nAu niveau des rglages additionnels ajouter la ligne : \nacceptance_as_validation: on\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidnadar\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ed5d7c908edb94af455554bf3af52d53?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ed5d7c908edb94af455554bf3af52d53?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidnadar\" class=\"reviewer-name\">davidnadar</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin is good for creating contact forms for your WordPress website.\nAnd this plugin is easy to use &amp; understandable.  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div c