n.com\">ThemeFusion | Professional Website Tools</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"John Hughes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23545:\"<div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-3 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\"  style=\'background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;\'><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row \"><div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1 fusion-builder-column-3 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last 1_1\"  style=\'margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\'>\n					<div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\">\n						<div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/reviews/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Customer reviews</a> play an essential role in online marketing. Reviews help your business establish credibility and influence consumers buying decisions. You can hope that customers impressions of your products are enough to motivate them to leave reviews. However, you may not get the results you want by using a passive approach. A more effective strategy is to <a href=\"https://starfish.reviews/the-best-ways-to-ask-customers-for-reviews/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ask for reviews on Google</a>. Many people are willing to share positive feedback about companies theyre satisfied with, especially if they know that their opinions will be appreciated. Often, all it takes is a gentle push or reminder.</p>\n<p>In this post, well explain the benefits of encouraging customer reviews on Google. Then well walk you through three steps for using your <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> WordPress website to generate more Google reviews via a plugin. Lets get started!</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-15 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Why Its Beneficial to Ask for Reviews on Google</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/reviews/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Customer reviews</a> are an effective way to establish credibility as a business for your products and services. More than that, they can also help to:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-5\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#5e5e5e;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Boost natural search for particular search terms related to your business</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#5e5e5e;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Boost Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#5e5e5e;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Drive traffic to your website</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#5e5e5e;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Improve customer trust through transparency</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#5e5e5e;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Provide social proof</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:10px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Google Reviews, in particular, can help <a href=\"https://starfish.reviews/how-online-reviews-help-your-local-seo/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">improve local SEO for your business</a>. Lets say that someone searches on Google for nearby restaurants:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-7 hover-type-none\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[de4c9717278ee855032]\" data-title=\"Google Maps Local Restaurants\" title=\"Google Maps Local Restaurants\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor.jpg\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1027\" alt=\"Google Maps Local Restaurants\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-679883\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271800%27%20height%3D%271027%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201800%201027%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271800%27%20height%3D%2731027%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor-200x114.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor-400x228.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor-600x342.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor-800x456.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor-1200x685.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/local-restaurants-boston-compressor.jpg 1800w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 1800px\" /></a></span><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>In most cases, theyll look more favorably on the establishments/businesses/services that display many positive reviews. Consumer reviews help demonstrate that a business is a popular place and that the majority of people have had a good experience there. Fortunately, Google makes the process of leaving a review simple and straightforward.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-16 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">How to Use Your Avada Website to Generate More Google Reviews (In 3 Steps)</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Once you understand the benefits of customer reviews, its time to figure out how to generate them for your <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> website. Lets take a look at three steps you can take to drive Google reviews through your <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">website</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:10px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-17 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> Install a Reviews Plugin On Your Avada Website</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://starfish.reviews/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Starfish Reviews</a> is a plugin designed to help you collect and display customer feedback, reviews, and testimonials where prospects are most likely to see them.</p>\n<p>This tool customizes actions based on each specific customer. It lets you gain a better understanding of a customers experience and opinions before asking them to leave a Google review. With this strategy, you can direct happy customers who are ready to leave a positive review to the right place. Meanwhile, those who didnt have a pleasant experience can get support from your business to (hopefully) resolve the problem.</p>\n<p>You can start with the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-reviews/#installation\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">free version</a> of the plugin, and then go <a href=\"https://starfish.reviews/plans-pricing/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">premium</a> to get access to all of its features. If you opt for premium and once you purchase a <a href=\"https://docs.starfish.reviews/article/4-how-to-install-starfish-reviews\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">license</a>, youll receive an email with the information youll need. Then you can upload and install the plugin.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:10px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-18 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Create Your First Funnel</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>After you activate Starfish Reviews, its time to create your first <a href=\"https://docs.starfish.reviews/article/89-creating-your-first-funnel\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">funnel</a>. A funnel is a prompt that will ask customers about their experience with your business or service. You can configure the funnel settings to send customers to a specific URL based on their answers.</p>\n<p>To create a funnel, you can go to Starfish Reviews &gt; All Funnels in your WordPress dashboard, followed by clicking the Add New button. On this page, youll be able to add a funnel name, as well as your company logo, which will appear at the top of the funnel:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-8 hover-type-none\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel.png\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[fb219aeb1035fd13555]\" data-title=\"Starfish Funnel\" title=\"Starfish Funnel\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel.png\" width=\"773\" height=\"469\" alt=\"Starfish Funnel\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-672165\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27773%27%20height%3D%27469%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20773%20469%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27773%27%20height%3D%273469%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel-200x121.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel-400x243.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel-600x364.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/preview-funnel.png 773w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 773px\" /></a></span><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The following sections include funnel settings where you can input a yes/no question that determines where youll point customers to next. For example, you could ask: Would you recommend us?.</p>\n<p>You can also customize the response buttons. There are options to add thumbs, faces, or symbols:</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><span class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-9 hover-type-none\"><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27575%27%20height%3D%27300%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20575%20300%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27575%27%20height%3D%273300%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/starfish.gif\" width=\"575\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Customize Starfish Reviews\" title=\"Customize Starfish Reviews\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-672170\"/></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Also, on this page, you will find a funnel shortcode. You can copy and paste this code to use it on other pages and posts. Theres even a way to <a href=\"https://docs.starfish.reviews/article/100-how-to-embed-a-funnel-in-email-or-anywhere-on-the-web\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">embed</a> your funnels into emails. Also, there will be a box where you can add a response that users who leave a positive review will see. You can customize your answer, but it will likely be along the lines of Excellent! Please leave us a positive review on Google!</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:10px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-19 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Set Google as the Destination for Customer Reviews</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The final step is to choose where to send users who want to leave a positive review. After adding your response in the <strong><em>Review Prompt</em></strong> text box, you can select <strong><em>Single</em></strong> or <strong><em>Multiple</em></strong> from <strong><em>Number of Destinations</em></strong> the drop-down menu:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-10 hover-type-none\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt.png\" width=\"1060\" height=\"590\" alt=\"Positive Response Prompt\" title=\"Positive Response Prompt\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-672166\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271060%27%20height%3D%27590%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201060%20590%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271060%27%20height%3D%273590%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt-200x111.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt-400x223.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt-600x334.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt-800x445.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/positive-response-prompt.png 1060w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 1060px\" /></span><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>If you only want to use Google as a destination, you can do so by clicking on Single, then inputting your <a href=\"https://starfish.reviews/how-to-get-the-perfect-link-to-ask-for-google-reviews/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Google Business Page URL</a>. However, if you choose Multiple, you can add another option, such as Facebook:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-11 hover-type-none\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/review-preview.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/review-preview.png\" width=\"793\" height=\"449\" alt=\"Ratings on Google and Facebook\" title=\"Ratings on Google and Facebook\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-672167\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27793%27%20height%3D%27449%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20793%20449%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27793%27%20height%3D%273449%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/review-preview-200x113.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/review-preview-400x226.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/review-preview-600x340.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/review-preview.png 793w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 793px\" /></span><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The last section will be for <strong><em>Negative Responses</em></strong>. As with the <strong><em>Positive Responses</em></strong> section, you can tailor your message to unhappy customers. You can also ask for their names, email addresses, and other contact information:</p>\n</div><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-12 hover-type-none\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response.png\" width=\"994\" height=\"425\" alt=\"Negative Response Section\" title=\"Negative Response Section\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-672168\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27994%27%20height%3D%27425%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20994%20425%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27994%27%20height%3D%273425%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response-200x86.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response-400x171.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response-600x257.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response-800x342.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/negative-response.png 994w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 994px\" /></span><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Next, you can choose where the feedback will be emailed to. For example, if you have a support team, making sure the team receives and addresses these emails promptly to help boost your customer service. Once done, click on <strong><em>Publish</em></strong>, and your new funnel will be ready to go.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-20 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Conclusion</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Customer reviews are a powerful and cost-effective way to enhance your business&#8217; credibility. Sometimes, people get distracted and forget to leave feedback on their own. However, making the process straightforward and accessible can help to generate significantly more reviews.</p>\n<p>As we discussed in this article, there are three steps you can ta