t=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> website into an effective marketing platform. Let&#8217;s begin.</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-11 fusion-checklist-divider\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#whatishubspot\">What Is HubSpot?</a></div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#usehubspot\">Why Should Businesses Use HubSpot?</a></div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#toolshubspot\">The HubSpot Suite Of Features And Tools</a></div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#freehubspot\">The Free HubSpot WordPress Plugin</a></div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#installhubspot\">Installing The HubSpot Plugin With Avada</a></div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#marketinghubspot\">Marketing Forms, Popups, And Live Chat For Your Avada Site</a></div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"border-bottom-color:#e0dede\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#conclusion\">Conclusion</a></div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-40 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"whatishubspot\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">What Is HubSpot?</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>HubSpot is an inbound marketing and sales cloud-based software suite. Their tools and service offerings help companies and individuals attract visitors, convert leads, control their marketing efforts, manage their sales processes, and much more. According to HubSpot, <a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/inbound-marketing\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">inbound marketing</a> is defined as:</p>\n</div><style type=\'text/css\'>.reading-box-container-1 .element-bottomshadow:before,.reading-box-container-1 .element-bottomshadow:after{opacity:0.70;}</style><div class=\"fusion-reading-box-container reading-box-container-1\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><div class=\"reading-box\" style=\"background-color:#f6f6f6;border-width:1px;border-color:#f6f6f6;border-left-width:3px;border-left-color:var(--primary_color);border-style:solid;\"><div class=\"reading-box-additional\">\n<p>&#8220;The process of attracting customers through relevant and helpful content and adding value at every stage in your customer&#8217;s buying journey. With inbound marketing, potential customers find you through channels like blogs, search engines, and social media. Unlike outbound marketing, inbound marketing does not need to fight for potential customers&#8217; attention. By creating content designed to address the problems and needs of your ideal customers, you attract qualified prospects and build trust and credibility for your business.&#8221;</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div>\n\n					</div>\n				</div><div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3 fusion-builder-column-43 fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3\"  style=\'margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;\'>\n					<div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\">\n						<span class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-23 hover-type-none\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/inbound-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"HubSpot Inbound Methodology\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology.png\" width=\"1276\" height=\"1276\" alt=\"HubSpot Inbound Methodology\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-666125\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271276%27%20height%3D%271276%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201276%201276%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271276%27%20height%3D%2731276%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology-200x200.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology-400x400.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology-600x600.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology-800x800.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology-1200x1200.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/inbound-methodology.png 1276w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></span><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div>\n\n					</div>\n				</div><div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_2_3 fusion-builder-column-44 fusion-two-third fusion-column-last 2_3\"  style=\'margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;width:66.66%;width:calc(66.66% - ( ( 4% ) * 0.6666 ) );\'>\n					<div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\">\n						<div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-fu