i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Extensive knowledgebase</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Reporting and analytics</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-right fas\" style=\"color:#bcbcbc;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Conversational bots</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div>\n\n					</div>\n				</div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-12 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\"  style=\'background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;\'><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row \"><div  class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1 fusion-builder-column-57 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last 1_1\"  style=\'margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\'>\n					<div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;\"   data-bg-url=\"\">\n						<div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-47 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"freehubspot\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">The Free HubSpot WordPress Plugin</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>The <a href=\"http://bit.ly/333daS7\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HubSpot All-In-One Marketing  Forms, Popups, Live Chat</a> FREE WordPress plugin allows you to easily connect your WordPress site and HubSpot account. Once the plugin is installed, the <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PALhNm\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HubSpot tracking code</a> is added to your WordPress pages and posts. After that, you can access the array tools and analytics offered by HubSpot directly from your WordPress account.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-48 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"installhubspot\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Installing The HubSpot Plugin With Avada</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>HubSpot offers a full stack of software for marketing, sales, and customer service, with a completely free CRM at its core. It&#8217;s used by 56,500 companies in over 100 countries to grow their business. Installing and setting up this free plugin with <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> is straight forward; let&#8217;s get started:</p>\n<p>In your WordPress Dashboard, go to Avada &gt; Plugins, and you will see the HubSpot plugin in our <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-plugins-section-compressor.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rel=\"iLightbox\">recommended section</a>.</p>\n<p>Click to install the plugin, and it will only take a few seconds to complete. Once installed, you will see HubSpot appear in the WordPress Dashboard sidebar. Now you all that is required is to connect to your existing account or register your new free HubSpot account.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-25\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[879a94696542cb29b24]\" data-title=\"HubSpot Connect Page\" title=\"HubSpot Connect Page\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page.jpg\" width=\"2748\" height=\"2506\" alt=\"HubSpot Connect Page\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-666718\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272748%27%20height%3D%272506%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202748%202506%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272748%27%20height%3D%2732506%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page-200x182.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page-400x365.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page-600x547.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page-800x730.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page-1200x1094.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-page.jpg 2748w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 2748px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>If you are registering a new account with the HubSpot CRM and successfully set up, you can now use forms and live chat on your <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> website. In addition to that, you will be able to view traffic analytics and manage your contacts in the free HubSpot CRM.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-26\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[3b44ee38a967e3ec696]\" data-title=\"HubSpot Connection Success\" title=\"HubSpot Connection Success\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success.jpg\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1386\" alt=\"HubSpot Connection Success\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-666731\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271620%27%20height%3D%271386%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201620%201386%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271620%27%20height%3D%2731386%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success-200x171.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success-400x342.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success-600x513.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success-800x684.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success-1200x1027.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-connect-success.jpg 1620w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 1620px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-49 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"marketinghubspot\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Marketing Forms, Popups, And Live Chat For Your Avada Site</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Included in the free plugin are lead capture tools like forms, popups, live chat, and an integrated contact database (CRM). Once you grow your email list, you can also send email campaigns and manage your digital ads through HubSpot. All these features work immediately with no developer help needed.</p>\n<p>Here are a couple of examples of active usage of the HubSpot contact form and live chat configured and activated on the <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> SEO demo.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-50 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Contact Form Example</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Highly configurable, an array of templates to choose from, and easy to style to match your brand. Choose anything from contact forms, subscriber forms to popups.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-27\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[2daad89488914fd2369]\" data-title=\"HubSpot Contact Form\" title=\"HubSpot Contact Form\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form.jpg\" width=\"2704\" height=\"1742\" alt=\"HubSpot Contact Form\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-666766\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272704%27%20height%3D%271742%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202704%201742%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272704%27%20height%3D%2731742%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form-200x129.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form-400x258.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form-600x387.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form-800x515.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form-1200x773.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-contact-form.jpg 2704w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 2704px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-51 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Live Chat Example</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Make it easier for your team to have unlimited, personalized conversations at high volume. HubSpot&#8217;s live chat tool is fully integrated with a chatbot builder.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-28\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[24baaa4d10df164bb6f]\" data-title=\"HubSpot Live Chat\" title=\"HubSpot Live Chat\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat.jpg\" width=\"2884\" height=\"3158\" alt=\"HubSpot Live Chat\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-666767\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272884%27%20height%3D%273158%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202884%203158%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272884%27%20height%3D%2733158%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat-200x219.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat-400x438.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat-600x657.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat-800x876.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat-1200x1314.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/hubspot-livechat.jpg 2884w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 2884px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:50px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-52 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"conclusion\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Conclusion</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Avada + HubSpot is everything you need to launch effective marketing campaigns that will attract customers to your business and entice them into engaging with your brand and products. We will be expanding on and detailing all of the plugins features when activated with <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l3jd8A\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> in subsequent Blog posts so stay tuned.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div>\n\n					</div>\n				</div></div></div></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/turn-your-avada-website-into-a-marketing-powerhouse-with-hubspot/\">Turn Your Avada Website Into A Marketing Powerhouse With HubSpot</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theme-fusion.com\">ThemeFusion | Professional Website Tools</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://theme-fusion.com/turn-your-avada-website-into-a-marketing-powerhouse-with-hubspot/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:30:\"https://theme-fusion.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\